metadata.description:
Your favorite Rapper as a Poke card!!!

This is a RARE, rare one of one in a series of Rapper Legend Pokemon Rapper Cards. There will be a drop of 9 Legend Cards and 9 Living Legend Cards.

LEGEND DROP:

  1. DMX
  2. PAC
  3. BIG PUN
  4. EAZY E
  5. NIPSEY HUSSLE
  6. JUICE WRLD
  7. POP SMOKE
  8. LEFT EYE
  9. AALIYAH

-----------

I was inspired to make this series of ‘PokeRapper’ by my current obsession with recovering my long lost Pokemon Card Collection and my long running love of hip hop.

LIVING-LEGEND DROP:

  1. EMINEM
  2. XZIBIT
  3. NAS
  4. JAY Z
  5. BEYONCE
  6. POLO G
  7. ****to be revealed
  8. ****to be revealed
  9. ****to be revealed

 ------------

Copyright notes: I have created this template by hand as a reproduction and tribute to Pokemon. I also offer custom card creations.
